        "10-changelog": {
            "name": "^o.book.name.changelog",
            "text": "§qv1.0.1§r§l:§r Bug Fix 1\n\nFull changelog at gm1.ca/support \n\n§1Change§r:\n\n - Characters can break more blocks. \n - Rings now stay on the ground longer after dropping them. \n\n§1Fix§r: \n - Characters can now home to the ender dragon. \n - Players should no longer get stuck half transformed. \n - Warp Rings no longer randomly teleport players. \n - Warp Rings no longer teleport players into the sky. \n - Various animation fixes.",
